related_questions.snippet: Lime peel exhibits antibacterial and antifungal properties. Research has shown it can significantly inhibit the growth of antibiotic-resistant bacteria and combat drug-resistant fungal infections that cause skin problems. Lime peel can enhance immune system functionality due to its flavonoid and vitamin C content.

related_questions.question: How do you make lime peel oil?
related_questions.title: Instructions
list: zest only the green outer part of the lime skin, be careful to avoid the pith of the lime.
next, place lime zest into a mason jar.
add 2 tablespoons of olive oil to the mason jar & stir ingredients.
put the lid on the jar and let the oil and peel sit for several hours.
